'''Remember Derra Squadron''' was a [[Starfighter/Legends|starfighter]] [[Squadron/Legends|squadron]] that served in the [[New Republic Starfighter Corps/Legends|New Republic Starfighter Corps]] flying [[BTL-S3 Y-wing starfighter/Legends|BTL-S3 Y-wing starfighters]].

The squadron was named in remembrance of the [[Battle of Derra IV]], during which a [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]] convoy bearing weapons and supplies meant for the new [[Echo Base/Legends|Echo Base]] on [[Hoth/Legends|Hoth]] was massacred by an [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] task force which included the [[181st Imperial Fighter Wing/Legends|181st Imperial Fighter Wing]].

In [[13 ABY/Legends|13 ABY]], the squadron participated in the [[Battle of Adumar]] as part of a New Republic fleet sent to reinforce [[General/Legends|General]] [[Wedge Antilles/Legends|Wedge Antilles]]' forces already stationed on the planet. During the battle, the Y-wings scored damaging hits on two of the [[Imperial-class Star Destroyer/Legends|Star Destroyers]] of the invading Imperial force.

